 <div type="translation" resp="part:argr part:wjsa">
           <p>Hail! Elapsed Śaka year 923, month of Jyeṣṭha, fifth <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>tithi</foreign></supplied>, waxing <supplied reason="explanation">fortnight</supplied> <supplied reason="explanation">25 May 901</supplied>. <supplied reason="subaudible">It was</supplied> the time of <supplied reason="subaudible">establishment of</supplied> this hermitage for/by the one named Śaruṅga.</p>
         </div>
